<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FinanceTracker - Bienvenue</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #8B5CF6;
      --primary-strong: #7C3AED;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(2,6,23,.12);
      --radius: 20px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { height: 100%; }
    body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ede9fe, #e0e7ff); display: grid; place-items: center; padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem); }

    .auth-shell { width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #eef2ff; border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow); overflow: hidden; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; min-height: 70dvh; }

    /* Panel gauche avec dégradés organiques */
    .panel-left { position: relative; background: linear-gradient(140deg, #f5d0fe 0%, #c4b5fd 35%, #8b5cf6 75%); display: grid; place-items: center; padding: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem); }
    .blob { position: absolute; inset: 0; background:
      radial-gradient(120% 80% at 20% 15%, rgba(255,255,255,.35), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(85% 65% at 80% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,.25), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(70% 60% at 30% 85%, rgba(255,255,255,.2), transparent 60%);
      mix-blend: overlay;
    }
    .welcome { position: relative; color: #fff; text-align: left; width: min(520px, 90%); }
    .welcome h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.2vw, 3.4rem); line-height: 1.05; margin: 0; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15); }
    .welcome .brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap:.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; opacity: .95; font-weight: 700; }

    /* Panel droit contenu */
    .panel-right { background: #fff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem); }
    .content { width: min(520px, 92%); }
    .content h2 { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.4vw, 1.8rem); margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .content p { color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
    .actions { display: flex; gap: .75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .6rem; padding: .9rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #fff; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(2,6,23,.04); }
    .btn:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(2,6,23,.08); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: transparent; box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139,92,246,.35); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-strong); }
    .helper { margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .helper a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .auth-shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
      .panel-left { min-height: 38dvh; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="auth-shell">
    <div class="panel-left">
      <div class="blob"></div>
      <div class="welcome">
        <div class="brand"><i class="fas fa-wallet"></i> FinanceTracker</div>
        <h1>Welcome
          <br/>
          Back!</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="panel-right">
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Bienvenue</h2>
        <p>Connectez-vous à votre compte ou créez-en un nouveau pour commencer à suivre vos finances.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Se connecter</a>
          <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Créer un compte</a>
        </div>
        <div class="helper">Nouveau ici ? <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}">Inscription</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 